description: Hang Seng China A Share ETF Series - Hang Seng China A Industry Top Index ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by Hang Seng Investment Management Limited. The fund invests in the public equity markets of China. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the stocks of large-cap companies. It seeks to replicate the performance of Hang Seng China A Industry Top Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. Hang Seng China A Share ETF Series - Hang Seng China A Industry Top Index was formed on November 12, 2013 and is domiciled in Hong Kong.
name: Hang Seng China A Industry Top Index ETF
